<pdd-reason>Discovers required model credentials across shell, environment, and PDD configuration sources.</pdd-reason>

<pdd-interface>
{
  "type": "module",
  "module": {
    "functions": [
      {"name": "scan_environment", "signature": "() -> Dict[str, KeyInfo]", "returns": "Dict[str, KeyInfo]"},
